# Cursor Rule — Frontend React

Use React JavaScript components.
Use React Router v6 for routes.
Use TanStack Query for server data.
Use Zustand for auth/UI state.
Use React Hook Form + Zod for forms.
Use DaisyUI components and Tailwind classes.
Use `StatusBadge` for statuses.
Do not hardcode API base URL.
